        "action": "Set minimum standards for schools policies regarding bullying and help",
        "additional_details": "Our schools need to be held accountable. There need to be minimum standards and they should be held to account if they fail to do enough to intervene with pupils or with parents. They need to encourage parents to communicate with their children.",
        "background": "Too many children are dying due to bullying, it needs to stop, I\u2019m a survivor, I still having issues even now and then I am hurting every time I hear another child has taken their life. Schools\u2019 policies need to teach pupils what is unacceptable/acceptable and support victims.",
